I"R<h1 id="user-authentication">User Authentication</h1>

<p>A person who intends to use the the JMTS must be authenticated and become an <strong>authorized user</strong> by doing the following:</p>

<ol>
  <li>Open a browser then enter the JMTS address (e.g. http://localhost/jmts) into the address field of the browser.</li>
  <li>When the Login Dialog appears, type a valid username and password then press the Login button as shown in the Figure 1 below.</li>
  <li>A person whose login attempt is validated will be directed to their ‘Home’ page of the JMTS.</li>
</ol>

